Cell.Text: S|Stendarr's Mercy. You found it. Azura's Star. | Maybe this is my chance to make things right. I can finish Malyn's work, the way we had meant to before his madness. | It would mean cutting the Star off from Azura. Only black souls would be able to enter it once we finished.
Are you ready to give me the Star?

Node.Caption: DA01NelacarStarBranchTopic: I have Azura's Star.

Cell.Text: The Star is being used to sustain Malyn's soul. I can't fix it while that fragment of him is inside.

Precisely. But it's not as simple as enchanting Malyn away. He's put up barriers. Souls are only allowed in, not out. | If we were to... somehow... send a soul inside the Star. One that was ready to overpower Malyn from the inside....

Node.Caption: DA01NelacarStarTopic01: So we need to deal with Malyn somehow.

Cell.Text: [S] I understand if you need some time to prepare. Let me know when you're ready.
A special type of soul trap. Placing you inside the Star without fully killing you. Once Malyn has been dealt with, I'll bring you back.

Node.Caption: DA01NelacarStarTopic03: You want to send my soul inside, don't you?

Cell.Text: I could soul trap you. Place you inside the Star. Then bring you back once Malyn has been dealt with.

Node.Caption: DA01NelacarStarTopic02: I don't like where this is going.

Cell.Text: Malyn's soul is beyond hope because his body is dead. But I'll be keeping you just slightly alive on this end. | But be careful. If you die inside the Star, your soul will be disrupted. There's nothing anyone can do for you if that happens.

Node.Caption: DA01NelacarStarQuestionsValasBranchTopic: What's to keep me from ending up like Malyn?

Cell.Text: Malyn's soul should be in the Star. Theoretically, purging him will be just like killing a ghost anywhere else. | I'll have a magical tether to your soul while you're inside. Once you're done, it'll be as simple as pulling you back into your body.

Node.Caption: DA01NelacarStarQuestionsInsideBranchTopic: What do I do once I'm inside?

Cell.Text: [S] G|Okay. Stand real still. This might sting.

Node.Caption: DA01NelacarReadyBranchTopic: I'm ready to enter the Star.

Cell.Text: He's already dead. Worse, the enchantment keeping him intact requires black souls. I don't know how many people he must have killed. | If we don't do something, the enchantment will fade, and the Star will slip back into Oblivion. Azura will have the last laugh.
[S] G|Give me a minute to examine the Star. I'll see what we'll need to do.

Cell.Text: All right, but hurry. Who knows if Azura if watching us?

Node.Caption: DA01NelacarStarChoice02: I'd like to think about it.
